originalText.text:
This business is a FRAUD. I was searching hours online to make this review but could not find it because it was listed as PERMANENTLY CLOSED‼️ BUT YET THE BUSINESS PHONE NUMBER WAS UPDATED 1 WEEK AGO. WHY WOULD "CLOSED" BUSINESS NEED TO UPDATE THEIR NUMBER. I took take a picture because I was actually at this store on December 13th 2023 and the reason for me taking the picture is because I work in the area. For the past 3 weeks I have been stopping at this Grocery Store Deli before work to get the same order. Curly fries $3 + Mozzarella sticks $4= $7. So I'm paying the same price for 3 weeks. Now it's 12/13/23 I get the same order and it's $8 all because I ask for one(1) Ketchup. After I already tapped my card then noticed the extra dollar plus tax charge. Keep in mind the sign still has the same prices. So I told them I won't be back. I think the man behind the counter name is (MO) WHICH IS ALSO THE OWNER Arab guy. MEXICAN GUY making the food in just deciding any price they want to give to a person. My thing is if sauce is extra money why can you have that written somewhere? I work very hard for my money and a dollar adds up. I'm not going to have any one take advantage of me or steal from me. So I'm in the process of DISPUTING THE WHOLE CHARGE ON MY CREDIT CARD NOW YOU GET NOTHING FROM ME. IM ALSO CALLING 311 TO REPORT THE BUSINESS.
ALSO THIS STORE IS DOING ILLEGAL ACTIVITIES*** THE OWNER HAD A BOOK TO THE LEFT SIDE OF HIM THAT HE WRITE IN BECAUSE HE IS GIVING PEOPLE CREDIT!!!!
THE ARE ALSO LETTING PEOPLE GET HOT FOOD ON FOOD STAMPS IF THEY KNOW YOU.
IM TAKING THIS AND POSTING IT EVERY WHERE. I BELIEVE ITS KARMA.
